      • addDefinition

        public void addDefinition(Definition definition)
        Add Definition to this repository.

        It compares values of Definition.getDefinitionId() of existing definition instances with the given definition. If the same definitionId already exist, then it will merge them. Otherwise, it will simply add the instance to this repository.

        Parameters:
        definition -
